SELECT distinct employmentenddate, IngestionDate, validto, IsActive FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] where employeeid = 500483 order by ingestiondate
select distinct leaving, expected_From from [odw_standardised_db].[dbo].[hr_leavers] where pers_no = 500483 order by expected_from

select distinct employmentenddate, employeeid   FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] where isactive= 'Y' AND WorkC NOT IN ('AG', 'CT', 'LU', 'NO', 'NS') order by employeeid
select count(*) FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] where isactive= 'Y' AND WorkC NOT IN ('AG', 'CT', 'LU', 'NO', 'NS')

SELECT DISTINCT IngestionDate from [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim] order by IngestionDate

SELECT
    employeeid, EmploymentEndDate, COUNT(*)
FROM
     [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[hr_employee_leavers_dim]
WHERE IsActive = 'Y'
GROUP BY
     employeeid, EmploymentEndDate
HAVING 
    COUNT(*) > 1
